### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/organizations/1/members
@token = Bearer {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}

### Ajouter un membre (invite)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jean.dupont@example.com",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}

### Ajouter un stagiaire
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "julie.martin@example.com",
  "role": "INTERN"
}

### Lister les membres
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### Changer le role d'un membre
PUT {{baseUrl}}/2/role
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "MANAGER"
}

### Accepter une invitation
POST {{baseUrl}}/accept
Authorization: {{token}}

### Retirer un membre
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/2
Authorization: {{token}}

### Quitter l'organisation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/leave
Authorization: {{token}}
